sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as MLflow SDK Client
    participant Browser as Browser (ODH Dashboard)
    participant Gateway as ODH Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant MLflow as MLflow Server<br/>5000/TCP HTTP (TLS at pod)
    participant K8sAuth as kubernetes-auth Plugin
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP TLS 1.2+
    participant S3 as S3-compatible Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: User SDK Request (Experiment Tracking)
    Client->>Gateway: POST /mlflow/api/2.0/mlflow/runs/create<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (K8s SA)
    Gateway->>MLflow: Forward HTTP/5000<br/>Bearer Token forwarded
    MLflow->>K8sAuth: Authenticate request
    K8sAuth->>K8sAPI: POST SelfSubjectAccessReview<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>K8sAuth: Allowed (mlflow.kubeflow.org)
    K8sAuth-->>MLflow: Auth OK + workspace resolved
    MLflow->>PG: INSERT run record<br/>Auth: Username/password
    PG-->>MLflow: Row inserted
    MLflow-->>Gateway: 200 OK (run_id)
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: Artifact Upload
    Client->>Gateway: POST /mlflow/api/2.0/mlflow-artifacts/artifacts/*<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Gateway->>MLflow: Forward HTTP/5000
    MLflow->>K8sAuth: Authenticate request
    K8sAuth->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview
    K8sAPI-->>K8sAuth: Allowed
    MLflow->>S3: PUT object<br/>Auth: AWS IAM / HMAC
    S3-->>MLflow: 200 OK
    MLflow-->>Gateway: 200 OK
    Gateway-->>Client: Upload confirmed

    Note over Browser,S3: Flow 3: UI Access (Embedded in Dashboard)
    Browser->>Gateway: GET /mlflow/<br/>Auth: Browser session (Bearer Token)
    Gateway->>MLflow: Forward HTTP/5000
    MLflow-->>Gateway: React UI (index.html + static assets)
    Gateway-->>Browser: HTML/JS/CSS
    Browser->>Gateway: GET /mlflow/ajax-api/2.0/mlflow/experiments/list<br/>X-MLFLOW-WORKSPACE + Authorization headers
    Gateway->>MLflow: Forward with headers
    MLflow->>K8sAuth: Authenticate (workspace-scoped)
    K8sAuth->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview
    K8sAPI-->>K8sAuth: Allowed
    MLflow->>PG: SELECT experiments
    PG-->>MLflow: Result set
    MLflow-->>Gateway: JSON experiments list
    Gateway-->>Browser: Render experiments

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 4: OpenTelemetry Trace Ingestion
    participant OTel as OTel Collector / SDK
    OTel->>Gateway: POST /v1/traces<br/>Auth: Bearer Token + x-mlflow-experiment-id
    Gateway->>MLflow: Forward HTTP/5000
    MLflow->>K8sAuth: Authenticate (experiment-scoped)
    K8sAuth->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview
    K8sAPI-->>K8sAuth: Allowed
    MLflow->>PG: INSERT trace spans<br/>Auth: Username/password
    PG-->>MLflow: Stored
    MLflow-->>Gateway: 200 OK
    Gateway-->>OTel: Trace accepted
